channel.title: ZoSo Skillcape. First model
channel.description:
Some people may know what ZoSo is, But if you don't its the symbol of Jimmy Page. Anyway heres a skillcape I made with his symbol.
Couple things The base of the skillcape is the music cape. The symbol could be down more and bigger. But its my first model so probably will do a V2 and more sometime soon.
[IMG]http://i393.photobucket.com/albums/pp11/leavenow1/ZosoCape.png[/img]
